INSERT INTO `tb_sys_note` VALUES (1, 1, '管理员', '你还不会穿搭毛呢大衣外套吗？小编来告诉你', '1', 1, '高定双排扣商场同款咖色百搭经典双面呢羊毛中长款大衣风衣款外套', '知性', '<p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(37, 53, 69);\">毛衣属于冬季存在感最强的一件单品，主要是因为它的价格大多数都比较平价，而且和羽绒服以及大衣相比更加百搭耐穿一些，所以当我们在穿这种平价毛衣的时候，也可以去试一下不同的技巧，下面就让我们继续看看时尚博主的精彩演绎，她们的穿搭更具有高级感，而且不容易撞衫。</span></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><br/></p><h3 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%;\">思路一：根据毛衣的材质</h3><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://pics4.baidu.com/feed/8718367adab44aede7dd1ea147433a08a08bfb4a.jpeg@f_auto?token=fab008361ac4e0f8f4cd46befa669e9a\" width=\"640\" class=\"_1mscr\"/></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%;\">在很多人的心理肯定会想：&quot;毛衣不都长得差不多吗？在材质上还有什么好选择的！&quot;其实毛衣的材质有很多的讲究，比如不同粗细线的毛衣，针织出来的效果就非常不同。</span><span style=\"max-width: 100%;\">即使是采用了一个款式，选择不一样的毛线，能够让一件款式出来两种不同的效果，所以一定要学会该怎么</span><strong style=\"max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\">选择毛衣的材质</strong><span style=\"max-width: 100%;\">。</span></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%;\">首先我们一定要记住的是，想要让毛衣更加有型，选择粗线肯定没错，但与之带来的粗针毛衣会更加硬挺显胖，这是不能够避免的面料效果。</span></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><br/></p><h3 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%;\">思路二：根据毛衣的款式</h3><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://pics2.baidu.com/feed/b2de9c82d158ccbfd452c060ed870137b0354163.jpeg@f_auto?token=618dffd8ca39c157bb0cc3ae9cf34aab\" width=\"640\" class=\"_1mscr\"/></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%;\">表面制作的比较细致的毛衣不可选，那是不是毛线质感越明显？表面越粗糙的毛衣穿搭效果就越好呢？其实也不尽然，所谓物极必反，任何一种元素，只要使用过于频繁或者分寸把握不当都有可能让整体穿搭毁于一旦。细致的毛衣质感整体会给人带来臃肿感，而毛线突出的毛衣会在细节上带来臃肿感。</span></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><br/></p><h3 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%;\">思路三：根据毛衣的长度</h3><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://pics5.baidu.com/feed/96dda144ad3459820b1224ab08948ca4caef84dd.jpeg@f_auto?token=e62ece11a637983da3aab4057eb68b4a\" width=\"640\" class=\"_1mscr\"/></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%;\">毛衣的长度也是有讲究的，太短的毛衣下摆会被撑起来，显得胸部更突出。太长的则会显得上半身都是圆圆的，看起来很臃肿。可以选择大领口短款带点收腰的或者前短后长的毛衣（长款毛衣将衣服前面下摆往里扎一些，一样能轻松打造前短后长的时髦感），很适合大胸女生。</span></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><br/></p><h3 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%;\">思路四：秋冬季节毛衣怎么穿才时髦</h3><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%;\">tips1：毛衣+百褶裙</strong></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://pics6.baidu.com/feed/3b87e950352ac65c72ec1ec30fad0f1892138a7a.jpeg@f_auto?token=855e705716e3e23c68594db1f96328cc\" width=\"640\" class=\"_1mscr\"/></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: justify;\">毛衣的款式对于我们来来说，的确是很受欢迎的款式，而且毛衣本身就是比较温柔一点，在秋冬季节的搭配也不会显得寒冷，而且毛衣的外套也是相对比较能保暖一点，所以也成为了很多人选择的必选款式，秋冬的第一件衣服，很多人都会买毛衣。</span></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: justify;\">而且还有非常大的优点，就是毛衣的温柔，无论是毛衣款式本身，还是我们拿出来穿搭，都非常的知性温柔，而且很大方的感觉，把女性的很多温柔都穿在了身上。</span></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%;\">tips2：毛衣+印花裙</strong></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://pics1.baidu.com/feed/738b4710b912c8fcc623d01f085c2f4cd48821fc.jpeg@f_auto?token=fe952d152a202ed8b5d9aea6b9ae3ed2\" width=\"640\" class=\"_1mscr\"/></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px; overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; text-align: justify; padding: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%;\">一组成功的造型，上衣和下装缺一不可，二者之间的协调与匹配更是决定了造型是否翻车的关键。采用毛衣作为上装时，若是利用碎花裙与之匹配，色彩的平衡则是要牢牢把控的重点。</span></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px; overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; text-align: justify; padding: 0px !important;\">毛衣采取的是冷色调，碎花裙中也带有明显的蓝色，二者之间的搭配会更加默契。碎花裙原本的外观就能够形成无数种变化，不管是色彩的不同，还是碎花图案的大小，都能够让裙装的整体样式大变样。在利用毛衣和碎花裙的组合时，只要记住颜色之间形成呼应，就很难有搭配失手的可能。</p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%;\">tips3：毛衣+针织裙</strong></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://pics3.baidu.com/feed/dc54564e9258d10905e0a2d8250771b66d814dc6.jpeg@f_auto?token=21abcbf51e53ca05c7a26553319f47c7\" width=\"637\" class=\"_1mscr\"/></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%;\">针织裙的搭配，在秋冬季节也十分普遍，在天气没完全暖和的时候和换季时节，穿针织裙温度非常适宜。</span><span style=\"max-width: 100%;\">毛衣搭配同色的半身裙可以形成色彩上的一致性，针织裙由于面料柔软服帖，对身材比较挑剔。</span><strong style=\"max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\">如果你拥有苗条的身材，适合选择包臀裙的款式。身材不完美的女人，建议选宽松款式的针织裙更佳。</strong></p><p><br/></p>', NULL, 1, 1, 0, 2, NULL, '2c35d9ff77644684831e4e56ceb2847e.jpg', '2024-02-18 16:49:28', '2024-02-18 17:02:19');
INSERT INTO `tb_sys_note` VALUES (2, 1, '管理员', '“连衣裙”怎么穿更好看？这些穿搭干货要牢记，美到骨子里', '1', 13, '安妮不火温柔风碎花吊带裙女2023春季微胖收腰气质连衣裙打底裙子', '知性', '<p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%;\">夏天当然要穿连衣裙，简直是懒人搭配的福音，一件轻松搞定整套</span><span style=\"max-width: 100%;\">look。但是连衣裙到底应该怎么穿才好看？怎样才能穿出自己的时尚风格，拒绝“烂大街”的搭配，一定要牢记这些穿搭小tips，风格高级还能很好的修饰身材，干货满满赶快学起来！</span></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://pics1.baidu.com/feed/279759ee3d6d55fb9d75053d84d6984021a4dd7d.jpeg@f_auto?token=20bcaa4ffa89f1cb82ede2cee2b18b6f\" width=\"640\" class=\"_1mscr\"/></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><br/></p><h3 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%;\">【一】穿连衣裙一定要掌握正确的穿搭思路，兼具时尚感和功能性</h3><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%;\">1、 选对长度得体又时髦</strong></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%;\">想要把连衣裙穿得好看又得体，首先要选对连衣裙的长度。</span><strong style=\"max-width: 100%;\">个子娇小的女生</strong><span style=\"max-width: 100%;\">在选连衣裙时长度</span><strong style=\"max-width: 100%;\">尽量不要超过膝盖</strong><span style=\"max-width: 100%;\">，不要过多的遮挡身体线条，不仅会显得人拖沓又沉闷，还有可能会在视觉上</span></span><span style=\"max-width: 100%;\">“压制身高”。</span></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%;\">个子高挑的女孩</strong><span style=\"max-width: 100%;\">在选择连衣裙时也</span><strong style=\"max-width: 100%;\">尽量要选择“露出脚踝”的长度</strong><span style=\"max-width: 100%;\">，可以显得更加纤细挺拔，时髦度翻倍！</span></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://pics2.baidu.com/feed/b7fd5266d01609243546e8263ef3e2f0e7cd34af.jpeg@f_auto?token=e113c9618dfdd07ddffb460361d20210\" width=\"640\" class=\"_1mscr\"/></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%;\">2、 适度露肤更加显瘦，穿出十足的高级感</strong></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%;\">穿连衣裙时想要显瘦又保持氧气感的诀窍，就是要保持一定的</span><span style=\"max-width: 100%;\">“露肤感”。炎热的夏天当然就是要秀出好身材，显瘦又高级。</span></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%;\">推荐姐妹们可以尝试一下今年大火的</span><strong style=\"max-width: 100%;\">“挂脖式”连衣裙</strong><span style=\"max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%;\">，打破了传统带袖连衣裙的呆板沉闷，也要比吊带连衣裙具有更强的功能性。挂脖设计可以完美修饰脖颈部分的线条，非常</span><strong style=\"max-width: 100%;\">适合有斜方肌困扰的姐妹们</strong><span style=\"max-width: 100%;\">，修身又时髦！</span></span></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://pics4.baidu.com/feed/b64543a98226cffc96ee31dd5ff59d9af403ea9d.jpeg@f_auto?token=682b8bc249442c2859042dcf4d03d1be\" width=\"640\" class=\"_1mscr\"/></p><p></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%;\">3、 穿对颜色显白又吸睛，高级感再上一个台阶</strong><br/></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\">夏天当然要用颜色穿出穿出惊艳感，选对连衣裙的颜色不仅可以提升肤色，还可以在人群中瞬间脱颖而出，将氛围感直接拉满。</p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%;\">白皮的姐妹可以尝试下图中的</span><strong style=\"max-width: 100%;\">酒红色吊带连衣裙</strong><span style=\"max-width: 100%;\">，酒红色极具性感风情还可以很好的显白，轻松穿出</span></span><span style=\"max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%;\">“冷白皮”的效果，满满的高级感。</span><strong style=\"max-width: 100%;\">黄黑皮更推荐选择紫色的连衣裙</strong><span style=\"max-width: 100%;\">，但一定要注意</span><strong style=\"max-width: 100%;\">不要选择饱和度过高的紫色</strong><span style=\"max-width: 100%;\">，避免穿出“老气感”，紫色轻松可以打造出内敛又有质感的时髦范儿，吸睛又惊艳！</span></span></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://pics6.baidu.com/feed/b999a9014c086e0627e728b1eefcacfe08d1cbf8.jpeg@f_auto?token=d4d4d2c992c1579511cf0b5bae63d70f\" width=\"640\" class=\"_1mscr\"/></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%;\">4、 拉高腰线女人味十足，优雅又显高</strong></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\">腰线在身材比例中起着决定性的作用，在穿连衣裙时拉高腰线可以瞬间优化身材，就算是五五分的身材比例也能穿出高挑又气质的感觉。</p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%;\">在选择高腰线连衣裙时，为了打造出搭配的层次感和精致度，可以选择<strong style=\"max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%;\">裙量较大的A</span><span style=\"max-width: 100%;\">字形</span><span style=\"max-width: 100%;\">裙摆设计的连衣裙</span></strong>。通过松紧对比来突出层次，这样的组合方式也<strong style=\"max-width: 100%;\">非常适合梨形身材的姐妹</strong>，发挥身材优势，最大程度地</span><span style=\"max-width: 100%;\">扬长避短。</span></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: ce