flow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><span class=\"bjh-p\" style=\"max-width: 100%;\"><span class=\"bjh-strong\" style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-weight: 700;\">02.</span></span></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><span class=\"bjh-p\" style=\"max-width: 100%;\"><span class=\"bjh-strong\" style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-weight: 700;\">温柔淑女风</span></span></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><span class=\"bjh-p\" style=\"max-width: 100%;\">我平时出门时往往就会考虑这种风格，也是周末出游穿搭频率最高的一个风格。</span></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><span class=\"bjh-p\" style=\"max-width: 100%;\">注意<span class=\"bjh-strong\" style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-weight: 700;\">运用吊带突出女人味</span>，绝对能赋予了整体一股慵懒的特别魅力。<span class=\"bjh-br\" style=\"max-width: 100%; display: block;\"></span></span></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><span class=\"bjh-p\" style=\"max-width: 100%;\">吊带缎面的材质<span class=\"bjh-strong\" style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-weight: 700;\">减少</span>了纯色的<span class=\"bjh-strong\" style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-weight: 700;\">单调感</span>，搭配白色衬衫和黑色伞裙，非常能够迎合春天的美好氛围。<span class=\"bjh-br\" style=\"max-width: 100%; display: block;\"></span></span></p><p><img src=\"https://pics1.baidu.com/feed/d53f8794a4c27d1e1f0cc70cf8cff466dcc438f7.jpeg@f_auto?token=e65a933caab2e0efb17421d72c2df588\" width=\"640\" class=\"_1mscr\"/></p><p style=\