width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%;\">先送上这套清新感满满的浅色系穿搭。米色棉麻西装+白色T恤+直筒牛仔裤，</span><strong style=\"max-width: 100%;\">简单日常又很有气质</strong><span style=\"max-width: 100%;\">。</span></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><br/></p><p><img src=\"https://pics6.baidu.com/feed/6a63f6246b600c333dde262ffb84b006dbf9a181.jpeg@f_auto?token=33f3cd91de9fb910f107054cb5ec97ef\" width=\"640\" class=\"_1mscr\"/></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%;\">米色西装颜色百搭又不挑肤色，结合轻薄透气、有肌理感的棉麻材质</span><span style=\"max-width: 100%;\">（穿到夏天也是可以的）</span><span style=\"max-width: 100%;\">，瞬间有文青内味~</span></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><br/></p><p><img src=\"https://pics6.baidu.com/feed/f636afc379310a55f5311aad558da2a0832610a0.jpeg@f_auto?token=151e61bd9f167e2a3f9a55ec9e7c16fc\" width=\"640\" class=\"_1mscr\"/></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\">▲不过棉麻易皱，选择棉麻混纺的材质更实用</p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%;\">棉麻面料有一定的柔软和垂顺度，很遮肉，</span><strong style=\"max-width: 100%;\">超级适合微胖、上半身胖、肩宽背厚的姐妹。</strong></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\">但是因为棉麻本身就比较轻薄，最好不要挑选落肩款，有点太随意了。要带点小垫肩才能穿出气场。</p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><br/></p><p><img src=\"https://pics6.baidu.com/feed/8c1001e93901213f30b548cbb52fd7d82e2e9571.jpeg@f_auto?token=98a5f27054d3ca441190b6538994b43f\" width=\"640\" class=\"_1mscr\"/></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%;\">欧尼最经常用来搭配西装的就是T恤，</span><strong style=\"max-width: 100%;\">可以削弱西装的正式感，既休闲又时髦。</strong></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><br/></p><p><img src=\"https://pics6.baidu.com/feed/2cf5e0fe9925bc31373b5f8cbd176cb8ca137096.jpeg@f_auto?token=bc82e966bb2a3e8ab42a91da0b9d90ae\" width=\"640\" class=\"_1mscr\"/></p><p><img src=\"https://pics1.baidu.com/feed/9e3df8dcd100baa137b87328afd8581bcafc2edb.jpeg@f_auto?token=fb010ec7710d27629de4d781da13c64f\" width=\"640\" class=\"_1mscr\"/></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\">▲这样的白T恤大家可以多准备几件，</p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\">作为西装内搭很合适</p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\">下半身欧尼搭配的是一条浅蓝色的直筒牛仔裤，浅色系+牛仔材质很休闲，很符合棉麻西装的率性自由feel。</p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%;\">早春大家都喜欢浅色系、清新的穿搭，姐妹们可以多准备一些浅色牛仔裤，</span><strong style=\"max-width: 100%;\">搭配起来更和谐</strong><span style=\"max-width: 100%;\">。</span></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><br/></p><p><img src=\"https://pics0.baidu.com/feed/a71ea8d3fd1f41346904c11dc1d774c3d0c85ef1.jpeg@f_auto?token=ea8e539b30b64c9a52d701d4de0b74c9\" width=\"640\" class=\"_1mscr\"/></p><p><br/></p>', NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0, NULL, 'bc165a28c74c477f9b0325e18a24bd39.png', '2024-02-19 14:05:30', NULL);
INSERT INTO `tb_sys_note` VALUES (11, 2, 'jane', '吊带就该这样穿，太撩人了', '1', NULL, NULL, '知性', '<p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><span class=\"bjh-p\" style=\"max-width: 100%;\">辣妹风从去年开始就有火爆的苗头，随着气温渐渐升高，这种类型的穿搭再一次席卷时尚圈。</span></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><span class=\"bjh-p\" style=\"max-width: 100%;\">不管是什么类型的女孩子，尝试这种风格，都能展现出自己<span class=\"bjh-strong\" style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-weight: 700;\">性感</span>的那面。<span class=\"bjh-br\" style=\"max-width: 100%; display: block;\"></span></span></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><span class=\"bjh-p\" style=\"max-width: 100%;\">前两天我也挑战了一波辣妹穿搭，工作室的小伙伴直呼太飒了，今年夏天也一定要这样出门试试。</span></p><p><img src=\"https://pics4.baidu.com/feed/08f790529822720e9191b4a69dd1534ef21fab36.jpeg@f_auto?token=4229cf8d6fa52da6318845cad3f4d5e3\" width=\"640\" class=\"_1mscr\"/></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><span class=\"bjh-p\" style=\"max-width: 100%;\">细心的我发现，吊带是营造辣妹感必不可少的一件单品。<span class=\"bjh-br\" style=\"max-width: 100%; display: block;\"></span></span></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><span class=\"bjh-p\" style=\"max-width: 100%;\">大面积的露肤加上腰线的拉高，上身<span class=\"bjh-strong\" style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-weight: 700;\">显高又显瘦</span>，没有哪个女生会拒绝这样的自己。</span></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><span class=\"bjh-p\" style=\"max-width: 100%;\">今天粒粒就来安利一波<span class=\"bjh-strong\" style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-weight: 700;\">吊带穿搭</span>，除了甜辣感，日常也可以驾驭。</span></p><p><img src=\"https://pics0.baidu.com/feed/5366d0160924ab1825b73a47d3e0bfc57a890bc4.jpeg@f_auto?token=a4e889649a6f4b650e7c84d97828616e\" width=\"640\" class=\"_1mscr\"/></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><span class=\"bjh-p\" style=\"max-width: 100%;\"><span class=\"bjh-strong\" style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-weight: 700;\">01.</span></span></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><span class=\"bjh-p\" style=\"max-width: 100%;\"><span class=\"bjh-strong\" style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-weight: 700;\">娘man平衡风<span class=\"bjh-br\" style=\"max-width: 100%; display: block;\"></span></span></span></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><span class=\"bjh-p\" style=\"max-width: 100%;\">如果说辣妹风是把女人味演绎到底，那不妨换个思路，把女性味道浓郁的吊带和<span class=\"bjh-strong\" style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-weight: 700;\">正式、休闲风格的单品</span>相碰撞。</span></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><span class=\"bjh-p\" style=\"max-width: 100%;\">我选择的这件基础款白色吊带可塑性很强，搭配短款西装外套<span class=\"bjh-strong\" style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-weight: 700;\">可盐可甜</span>。</span></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><span class=\"bjh-p\" style=\"max-width: 100%;\">下半身pick卫裤，特别适合<sp