 style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\">在选择裙装时，姑娘们首先会将注意力集中在款式及装饰元素上，观察它是否符合自己的审美品味，从而往往忽略许多非常关键的小细节，比如材质的选择。舒适的面料不仅能够带给我们满分的穿着体验，同时还能影响到整体造型的最终呈现效果。</p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\">思路二：裙子的长度</p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><br/></p><p><img src=\"https://pics3.baidu.com/feed/6a63f6246b600c33d83978a7b1e8fd07d8f9a14e.jpeg@f_auto?token=89702e391fdce21b3045f75d802a0114\" width=\"640\" class=\"_1mscr\"/></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\">因为每个人的身高不同，所以我们适合的裙子长度也有所不同，但总的来说裙子长度可以根据裙摆到我们的身体位置来进行判断。</p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\">短裙最合适的长度是大概在大腿中部的位置；而中长裙最适合的长度是在膝盖以下，小腿肚子以上这个范围；长裙最适合的长度，那当然就是脚踝以上小腿肚子以下的范围了。</p><p><br/></p>', NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0, NULL, '54ebb6170a504af4aacd5d0f23d1ec7d.jpg', '2024-02-19 15:01:31', NULL);
INSERT INTO `tb_sys_note` VALUES (16, 2, 'jane', '让你美出新高度的连衣裙！夏季穿着时髦加分，一不小心惊艳四座', '1', NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><span class=\"bjh-p\" style=\"max-width: 100%;\">女性的标志性单品想必就是连衣裙了，绘画中突出特点便会使用长发与摇曳的裙摆。而夏季正是裙摆飞扬的季节，各种连衣裙的款式更是让人目不暇接，所以也让许多爱美女士既幸福又烦恼，幸福的是可以利用连衣裙修饰身材，让自己变得更加优雅美丽。烦恼的是款式太多，反而不知道如何去选择适合自己的，所以<span class=\"bjh-strong\" style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-weight: 700;\">今天我们就来盘点一下，连衣裙的时尚搭配方案。</span></span></p><p><img src=\"https://pics0.baidu.com/feed/d1160924ab18972baf209a7576af5d8e9f510ae4.jpeg@f_auto?token=4c7a6a2740ae62e9c56cd1c433df180a\" width=\"640\" class=\"_1mscr\"/></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><span class=\"bjh-p\" style=\"max-width: 100%;\"><span class=\"bjh-strong\" style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-weight: 700;\">纹理设计小心机</span></span></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><span class=\"bjh-p\" style=\"max-width: 100%;\">大多数人都会认为平整面料精致设计更加吸引人，但其实并不是。如今的时尚流行风格，并不在局限于一种类型。纹理设计不规则的凹凸感面料，其实更加适合日常生活，可以打破低调单品的单调，也可以为整个造型增添个性与时尚。</span></p><p><img src=\"https://pics5.baidu.com/feed/0823dd54564e92587d63f28f0de0f75fcdbf4ee1.jpeg@f_auto?token=4312afbb1aed179ca2d062abd6250212\" width=\"640\" class=\"_1mscr\"/></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><span class=\"bjh-p\" style=\"max-width: 100%;\"><span class=\"bjh-strong\" style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-weight: 700;\">同色系时尚</span></span></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><span class=\"bjh-p\" style=\"max-width: 100%;\">很多女生喜欢穿衣搭配，但是却不知道如何入手。其实有一个非常简便的方法，就是同色系的搭配。可以让简约连衣裙拥有层次感，但同时又不会显得突兀。</span></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><span class=\"bjh-p\" style=\"max-width: 100%;\">尤其是浅蓝色与海蓝色的相互呼应，更是证明了这一点。带有一点灰色的色调，使得整个搭配都充满了高级气质。</span></p><p><img src=\"https://pics5.baidu.com/feed/7acb0a46f21fbe09dcc12108fa022a348644adfd.jpeg@f_auto?token=54b60e879e5d4f205fcfa3c98b312904\" width=\"640\" class=\"_1mscr\"/></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><span class=\"bjh-p\" style=\"max-width: 100%;\"><span class=\"bjh-strong\" style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-weight: 700;\">性感优雅相融合</span></span></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><span class=\"bjh-p\" style=\"max-width: 100%;\">随着时尚流行的进一步增加，现如今的流行元素越来越多，一条连衣裙中也可以出现多种风格。比如复古风的设计便是如此，既可以拥有优雅的气质，也可以利用修身的剪裁，让其拥有性感的意味。所以虽然仅仅只是一条连衣裙，但是却也可以给人与众不同的效果。</span></p><p><img src=\"https://pics5.baidu.com/feed/f31fbe096b63f6240c39264f1726cdff1b4ca3fb.jpeg@f_auto?token=f3e6412bfd4c32ab31bcd57521632848\" width=\"640\" class=\"_1mscr\"/></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><span class=\"bjh-p\" style=\"max-width: 100%;\"><span class=\"bjh-strong\" style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-weight: 700;\">格子元素打破常规</span></span></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><span class=\"bjh-p\" style=\"max-width: 100%;\">格子元素一直都是经典元素，但是从近几年开始便从经典元素转为流行元素的，比如格子西装外套就是非常著名的代表。其实格子的连衣裙也有魅力所在，它的魅力可以让简约的单品变得更加丰富多彩，是不容小觑的存在。</span></p><p><img src=\"https://pics5.baidu.com/feed/8644ebf81a4c510f937e9c73f23b032ad52aa58e.jpeg@f_auto?token=ef1a9ef6d23db198d55bedaed74108dc\" width=\"640\" class=\"_1mscr\"/></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><span class=\"bjh-p\" style=\"max-width: 100%;\"><span class=\"bjh-strong\" style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-weight: 700;\">复古排扣的小心机</span></span></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><span class=\"bjh-p\" style=\"max-width: 100%;\">人人都知道排扣的设计是复古风流行的趋势，尤其是与方领蓬蓬袖等元素结合，排扣的设计不仅影响风格属性，更可以修饰个人身材。从另一个视角介入的话就会发现，排扣设计与竖条纹有异曲同工之妙，所以都可以起到显瘦的效果。</span></p><p><img src=\"https://pics4.baidu.com/feed/a8ec8a13632762d0532641a2328e2efd513dc679.jpeg@f_auto?token=c09388082e231e85af19d054b5ecd1a0\" width=\"640\" class=\"_1mscr\"/></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><span class=\"bjh-p\" style=\"max-width: 100%;\"><span class=\"bjh-strong\" style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-weight: 700;\">知性休闲风</span></span></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><span class=\"bjh-p\" style=\"max-width: 100%;\">已经上班的女性觉得学生时代的单品，但其实并不是如此。有的单品看起来优雅知性，但其实学生党也可以穿着，相反也是如此。比如这种休闲式的格子连衣裙，兼有个性休闲，显得单调简约，但同时又与众不同，充满着设计感。</span></p><p><img src=\"https://pics0.baidu.com/feed/267f9e2f070828381b7db6b228fb8f064d08f189.jpeg@f_auto?token=cb3721cdeb37e5ff670dc4525f848c4e\" width=\"640\" class=\"_1mscr\"/></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><span class=\"bjh-p\" style=\"max-width: 100%;\"><span class=\"bjh-strong\" style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-weight: 700;\">吊带裙的叠穿</span></span></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><span class=\"bjh-p\" style=\"max-width: 100%;\">宽松版型的吊带裙对于身材没有特别大的束缚，加上深色的配色更容易显瘦。即使是身上肉肉很多的胖女生也可以完美驾驭，但是吊带裙有一个劣势，就是容易显得肩膀过于宽厚。所以我们可以叠穿宽松式的复古上衣，拥有优雅时尚的魅力，又能兼具显瘦的气质。</span></p><p><img src=\"https://pics3.baidu.com/feed/0b55b319ebc4b745bb33cd5c5f9e38108b8215ba.jpeg@f_auto?token=35f004b8638239fd0a72e583fc296dff\" width=\"640\" class=\"_1mscr\"/></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><span class=\"bjh-p\" style=\"max-width: 100%;\"><span class=\"bjh-strong\" style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-weight: 700;\">抽绳设计凹出好身材</span></span></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><span class=\"bjh-p\" style=\"max-width: 100%;\">搭配不好看并不一定是个人的问题，有时候是单品的问题。比如连衣裙中常见的抽绳设计就很有小心机，可以让你凹出好身材，看起来更加玲珑有致，瞬间拥有完美身材曲线。</span></p><p><img src=\"https://pics3.baidu.com/feed/d1a20cf431adcbeffb8d65383ecd08daa3cc9f38.jpeg@f_auto?token=a55bbcd70de68a5efa097ce2684c1d87\" width=\"640\" class=\"_1mscr\"/></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><span class=\"bjh-p\" style=\"max-width: 100%;\"><span class=\"bjh-strong\" style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-weight: 700;\">精致手拎包</span></span></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><span class=\"bjh-p\" style=\"max-width: 100%;\">看似不起眼的手拎包，其实也可以让造型与众不同，显得个性又时髦。尤其是具有设计感的手拎包更是如此，增添高级时尚。</span></p><p><img src=\"https://pics2.baidu.com/feed/d62a6059252dd42a45bf1ade92597db2c8eab8fe.jpeg@f_auto?token=848c1a9c364447aeb933d106a55a3bff\" width=\"640\" class=\"_1mscr\"/></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><span class=\"bjh-p\" style=\"max-width: 100%;\"><span class=\"bjh-strong\" style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-weight: 700;\">宽肩细腰</span></span></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><span class=\"bjh-p\" style=\"max-width: 100%;\">宽肩细腰加上大长腿，是很多女生都羡慕的身材。其实这种搭配也可以利用连衣裙构造，蓬蓬袖加上超级修身的高腰线，与看似可爱的蓬蓬的裙摆相互结合，那么便可以得到一个让人流口水的身材。</span></p><p><img src=\"https://pics2.baidu.com/feed/94cad1c8a786c917c56f2d88585f56c83ac757f8.jpeg@f_auto?token=ca7fab2db05abefddfcb6ba7e13e6203\" width=\"640\" class=\"_1mscr\"/></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><span class=\"bjh-p\" style=\"max-width: 100%;\">若隐若现的透视艺术，穿搭中非常常见，不仅不会显胖，反而可以显得优雅气质，更有女人味儿。</span></p><p><img src=\"https://pics6.baidu.com/feed/6a63f6246b600c33790278f2882e7708d9f9a17f.jpeg@f_auto?token=6504508065ab2037cc42ed7fe7004c44\" width=\"640\" class=\"_1mscr\"/></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><span class=\"bjh-p\" style=\"max-width: 100%;\">微胖女生选择裙装，可以选择中裙长裙，遮住多余的肉肉，以便起到整体显瘦的效果。</span></p><p><br/></p>', NULL, 1, 1, 32, 34, NULL, '8545b8e750be4c2793c41166cd36c745.png', '2024-02-19 16:56:38', NULL);
INSERT INTO `tb_sys_note` VALUES (17, 2, 'jane', '女人穿“小皮衣”有多靓丽，9种颜色皮衣搭配模板，飒酷且优雅呀', '1', NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\">春秋季节，时尚的小皮衣，也是女人们所钟爱的上衣之一。因为小皮衣带来的帅气、个性、飒酷风，往往能够搭配出超预期的效果，不同颜色的皮衣，搭配起来略有不同，本期糖果为大家分享<strong style=\"max-width: 100%;\">9种颜色小皮衣</strong>的常见搭配，一起来看看吧。</p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><br/></p><h3 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%;\">01 黑色皮衣</h3><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://pics4.baidu.com/feed/8b82b9014a90f60360a37296530e1e10b151edfc.png@f_auto?token=4c576734fc43a93423b30b753b717bff\" width=\"640\" class=\"_1mscr\"/></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%;\">黑色小皮衣 + 白色衬衫 + 牛仔裤</strong><span style=\"max-width: 100%;\">。在小皮衣颜色中，黑色是最常见的颜色，也是搭配起来最为简单的色彩，正如上图所示的搭配方式，内搭一件白色的衬衫，配上一件复古风格的牛仔裤，时髦感十足。</span></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><br/></p><h3 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%;\">02 墨绿色小皮衣</h3><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://pics7.baidu.com/feed/6d81800a19d8bc3efd1151b8d0970b15a8d3454a.png@f_auto?token=83723e5a0ad74c0dc26903c3478493bf\" width=\"640\" class=\"_1mscr\"/></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%;\">绿色短款小皮衣 + 黑色打底衫 + 黑色小脚裤 + 中筒靴</strong><span style=\"max-width: 100%;\">。优雅且时尚的绿色小皮衣，深色系，非常的称肤色。这款小皮衣采用的是短款设计，所以对女生的身高没有要求，就算是矮个子的女生，一样能穿出酷酷范儿。</span></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><br/></p><h3 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%;\">03 棕色皮衣</h3><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://pics6.baidu.com/feed/0b7b02087bf40ad16e1ee6680030bcd4a8ecce6e.png@f_auto?token=a6ae88b79887e5ba5b11d9d68c008411\" width=\"640\" class=\"_1mscr\"/></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%;\">棕色小皮衣 + 米色针织衫 + 深咖色百褶裙</strong><span style=\"max-width: 100%;\">。棕色的皮衣也是比较多见的，巧妙的使用同色系的搭配，让整体色彩搭配非常的和谐，就连和棕色的头发也是遥相呼应。</span></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><br/></p><h3 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%;\">04 米色小皮衣</h3><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://pics1.baidu.com/feed/0823dd54564e9258c26e2035cd9e7c53cdbf4ebe.png@f_auto?token=9e87dac89fa90fd899456c539b652c31\" width=\"640\" class=\"_1mscr\"/></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%;\">短款米色小皮衣 + 牛仔裤</strong><span style=\"max-width: 100%;\">。相比于纯白色，这种米白色的小皮衣更加柔和一些，更适合于中年成熟女性来穿，只需要搭配牛仔裤，已经足够好看了。</span></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><br/></p><h3 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%;\">05 姜黄色小皮衣</h3><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://pics4.baidu.com/feed/342ac65c10385343c1a498edc20f1d75cb8088be.jpeg@f_auto?token=9b34b84d422cd311787da31470f0834a\" width=\"640\" class=\"_1mscr\"/></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%;\">姜黄色短款皮衣 + A短皮裙 + 黑色皮靴</strong><span style=\"max-width: 100%;\">。非常有个性的搭配，皮衣+皮裤，或者搭配着蕾丝边风格的针织裙，女神范十足。</span></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://pics3.baidu.com/feed/29381f30e924b899ed1b8dcd041ab09e0b7bf6cc.png@f_auto?token=09ff53cfd2bddc98e7483a9fa4772a23\" width=\"640\" class=\"_1mscr\"/></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%;\">姜黄色皮衣 + 白色衬衫 + 白色短裤 + 白色平底鞋</strong><span style=\"max-width: 100%;\">。江疏影的这一身搭配，非常的显身材，色彩搭配上，恰到好处，色彩饱和度适中，给人一种非常舒适的感觉，无需滤镜就很有意境。</span></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><br/></p><h3 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%;\">06 红色小皮衣</h3><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://pics0.baidu.com/feed/377adab44aed2e7390d65ad7d81d0c8087d6fa32.png@f_auto?token=37fe143baf6167c6cc23e4bc8f9abd51\" width=\"640\" class=\"_1mscr\"/></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%;\">红色小皮衣 + 黑色打底衫 + 黑色小脚裤</strong><span style=\"max-width: 100%;\">。爱美之心人皆有之，尤其是成熟的女人，对穿衣搭配，事无巨细。巧妙地使用红黑搭配，搭配出高级感，时尚大气。</span></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><br/></p><h3 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%;\">07 粉色小皮衣</h3><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://pics2.baidu.com/feed/f9198618367adab4557acaddd5c81e178601e4aa.png@f_auto?token=26e6845dbda738150a64d3d24eb127c5\" width=\"640\" class=\"_1mscr\"/></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%;\">粉色皮衣 + 白色衬衫 + 白色裤子 + 运动鞋</strong><span style=\"max-width: 100%;\">。无论是什么衣服，只要和粉色沾边，一定会起到不错的减龄效果，小皮衣也不例外，这款淡粉色小皮衣外套，穿在身上，还是蛮抢镜的，走在街上，回头率一定蛮高的。</span></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><br/></p><h3 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%;\">08 豆绿色拼接皮衣</h3><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://pics3.baidu.com/feed/203fb80e7bec54e77a620e6adf24365b4ec26adb.png@f_auto?token=7071f4ba0a2bcdd2c4e7a026bd68eca4\" width=\"640\" class=\"_1mscr\"/></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\">豆绿色拼接皮衣 + 条纹衬衫 + 牛仔裤。非常有个性的一件皮衣外套，拼接款式，非常的洋气，搭配着同色系的衬衫牛仔裤，给人一种小清新的感觉。</p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><br/></p><h3 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%;\">09 咖色皮衣马甲</h3><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://pics4.baidu.com/feed/b21c8701a18b87d6122045745f1485331f30fd27.png@f_auto?token=ac65ed395ba3cb4629af47d2d46f0539\" width=\"640\" class=\"_1mscr\"/></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%;\">爵士咖皮衣马甲 + 白色衬衫 + 牛仔裤 + 长筒靴</strong><span style=\"max-width: 100%;\">。小众风格的皮衣马甲，作为今年的新款还是蛮洋气的。</span></p><p><br/></p>', NULL, 1, 1, 2, 4, NULL, '66c6c6f704884209a62ff00a9f0efc51.png', '2024-02-19 21:51:56', '2024-02-19 22:13:15');
INSERT INTO `tb_sys_note` VALUES (18, 2, 'jane', '是时候穿裙子了，送你几个连衣裙穿搭技巧，从款式到搭配全都有', '1', NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important; text-align: center;\"><span class=\"bjh-p\" style=\"max-width: 100%;\">与其它的服装相比，裙子对于女性来讲是有着不同的意义的，即使女性的搭配风格多种多样，裙子不再是唯一的选择，但是<span class=\"bjh-strong\" style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-weight: 700;\">裙子在女性心目中的地位和搭配出来的感觉就是很与众不同。</span></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://pics0.baidu.com/feed/d8f9d72a6059252d02db093c35525a335ab5b90f.jpeg@f_auto?token=5dab733fe74f8d96990316bca0fc7d01\" width=\"640\" class=\"_1mscr\"/></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important; text-align: center;\"><span class=\"bjh-p\" style=\"max-width: 100%;\">现在大多数的女性在参加一些隆重场合的时候都会选择穿裙装，这是对于场合的一种尊重和自己在心目当中对于时尚的追求。</span></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important; text-align: center;\"><span class=\"bjh-p\" style=\"max-width: 100%;\">所以，<span class=\"bjh-strong\" style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-weight: 700;\">即使现在有很多的风格将女性更偏于中性化，仍然阻挡不了女性对于裙子的喜爱。</span></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://pics4.baidu.com/feed/3b87e950352ac65ca2b33a9a173aeb1991138af2.jpeg@f_auto?token=66ee9312abf5d2907b758c3fb60d084d\" width=\"640\" class=\"_1mscr\"/></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important; text-align: center;\"><span class=\"bjh-p\" style=\"max-width: 100%;\">马上就要进入夏天了，裙子的选择变得更多了，该如何选择一条适合自己的裙子，又该进行怎样的搭配呢？<span class=\"bjh-strong\" style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-weight: 700;\">是时候穿裙子了，每日搭配指南送你几个连衣裙穿搭技巧，从款式到搭配全都有！</span></span></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important; text-align: center;\"><span class=\"bjh-p\" style=\"max-width: 100%;\">◎<span class=\"bjh-strong\" style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-weight: 700;\">本期内容小目录</span></span></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important; text-align: center;\"><span class=\"bjh-p\" style=\"max-width: 100%;\"><span class=\"bjh-strong\" style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-weight: 700;\">1、如何正确挑选适合自己的连衣裙</span></span></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important; text-align: center;\"><span class=\"bjh-p\" style=\"max-width: 100%;\"><span class=\"bjh-strong\" style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-weight: 700;\">2、不同款式的连衣裙如何搭配</span></span></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important; text-align: center;\"><span class=\"bjh-h3\" style=\"max-width: 100%; display: inline-block; position: relative; padding-left: 9px; font-weight: 700; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">如何正确挑选适合自己的连衣裙</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://pics7.baidu.com/feed/1e30e924b899a90176adf0fff15d53730008f5b4.jpeg@f_auto?token=0473b823a5f3d5a296912b8d850f3044\" width=\"640\" class=\"_1mscr\"/></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important; text-align: center;\"><span class=\"bjh-p\" style=\"max-width: 100%;\">无论是哪个年龄段的女性，穿裙子都会有一个共同的目标：<span class=\"bjh-strong\" style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-weight: 700;\">既显瘦又凸显时尚感，同时又能够彰显出自己的气质</span>。</span></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important; text-align: center;\"><span class=\"bjh-p\" style=\"max-width: 100%;\">裙装的选择和搭配相对是比较容易的，但是如果想要更加的精致，诠释出裙子与身体的契合度，还是要正确地挑选属于自己的连衣裙。</span></p><p style=\"overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important; text-align: center;\"><span class=\"bjh-p\" style=\"max-width: 100%;\"><span class=\"bjh-strong\" style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-weight: 700;\">① 偏瘦人群</span></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://pics3.baidu.com/feed/77c6a7efce1b9d16d3d4b5ab1e16ed878d54643d.jpeg@f_auto?token=852bbb994ca6713c047c2a6c915eedcd\" width=\"640\" class=\"_1mscr\"/></p><p><br/></p>', NULL, 1, 1, 0, 2, NULL, '1c244e229cf6422898593318061c8833.jpg', '2024-02-27 22:07:17', NULL);
INSERT INTO `tb_sys_note` VALUES (20, 2, 'jane', '短款“小皮衣”怎么搭配才好看？温柔又减龄的穿搭更有时尚味道', '1', NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; caret-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.498); font-size: 15px; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.75em; visibility: visible; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; letter-spacing: 1px; visibility: visible;\">黑色短款小皮衣配工装阔腿裤，经典而百搭的黑色小皮衣搭配绿色工装裤脚踩黑色高跟尖头鞋，简直太有气场了，再用白色上衣过渡一下整体简约大气又不失时尚度。搭配牛仔裤阔腿裤和纹衫，精致的法式风更是时尚味道。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: center; white-space: normal; caret-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.498); font-size: 15px; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); visibility: visible; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/jsp/upload?filePath=/ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20230227/1677508581210011766.png\" title=\"1677508581210011766.png\" alt=\"微信图片_20230227221640.png\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; caret-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.498); font-size: 15px; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.75em; visibility: visible; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; letter-spacing: 1px; visibility: visible;\">有衣品的女性在搭配时会用配饰来提升整体的时髦度，一个精致的包包，鞋子、帽子都可以给整体增加气质。如下图黑色短款小皮衣搭配条纹裤+报童帽，穿出一种今年主流的复古感，且有还有几分俏皮感，这里面使皮衣看着就没有那么硬朗了。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: center; white-space: normal; caret-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.498); font-size: 15px; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); visibility: visible; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/jsp/upload?filePath=/ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20240809/1723187687667052129.jpg\" title=\"1723187687667052129.jpg\" alt=\"1677508568707051929.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; caret-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.498); font-size: 15px; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.75em; visibility: visible; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; letter-spacing: 1px; visibility: visible;\">黑色短款小皮衣配九分裤，显高的同时还自带干练的通勤范，再配上一双尖头高跟鞋让整体的美看着更有气质。尽量选择有包容性的裤子，阔腿裤和直筒裤都是不错的选择，能够将腿部赘肉隐藏，这样更能显瘦。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: center; white-space: normal; caret-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.498); font-size: 15px; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); visibility: visible; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/jsp/upload?filePath=/ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20240809/1723187700443018409.jpg\" title=\"1723187700443018409.jpg\" alt=\"1677508568746004915.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; caret-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.498); font-size: 15px; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.75em; visibility: visible; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; letter-spacing: 1px; visibility: visible;\">黑色短款小皮衣配牛仔裤，这是小编姐姐贯穿的套路既简单又省时，内搭上衣也可以任意搭黑白T，印花雪纺衫、高领衫、蓝白色衬衫怎么出穿都不用担心出错。在穿搭上尽量上半身简单宽松，裤装可以选择紧身修身的裤子，这样才能更显身材。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: center; white-space: normal; caret-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.498); font-size: 15px; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/jsp/upload?filePath=/ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20240809/1723187712461067094.jpg\" title=\"1723187712461067094.jpg\" alt=\"1677508568746004915.jpg\"/><img src=\"/ueditor/jsp/upload?filePath=/ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20240809/1723187716416066584.jpg\" title=\"1723187716416066584.jpg\" alt=\"1677508568775060279.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; caret-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.498); font-size: 15px; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; caret-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.498); font-size: 15px; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p><p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; caret-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.498); font-size: 15px; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; letter-spacing: 1px;\">黑色短款小皮衣配宝蓝色百褶裙，走轻熟路线的姑娘们不妨尝试黑色短款小皮衣搭配宝蓝色百褶裙，优雅又易学的实用主义，可以作为早春气质的日常穿搭模板。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: center; white-space: normal; caret-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.498); font-size: 15px; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/jsp/upload?filePath=/ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20240809/1723187724369045356.jpg\" title=\"1723187724369045356.jpg\" alt=\"167750856880504902